<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>MyLibrary - Digital Library Management System</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css"/>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/static/favicon.png" />
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background-color: #f7f9fc;
      color: #333;
    }

    .navbar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      height: 60px;
      background-color: #183153;
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .nav-title {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .nav-title i {
      margin-right: 10px;
    }

    .nav-right {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .border {
      border: 1.5px solid transparent;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .border:hover {
      border: 1.5px solid white;
    }

    .btn {
      background: #1b75d0;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 13px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: rgb(20 110 190);
    }

    .hero-sec {
      background: linear-gradient(rgba(24, 49, 83, 0.6), rgba(24, 49, 83, 0.6)), url('http://localhost/lib/project/library.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
      min-height: 90vh;
      color: #fff;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .hero-sec h2 {
      margin-top: 100px;
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hero-sec p {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto 30px;
    }

    .hero-sec p strong {
      color: #ffcc00;
    }

    .hero-sec a {
      background-color: #ff9900;
      width: 300px;
      color: white;
      margin: 30px auto 0;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .hero-sec a:hover {
      background-color: #e88e00;
    }

    .features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
      padding: 60px 40px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .feature-box {
      background: #f2f7ff;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .feature-box:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      background-color: #eaf2ff;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .feature-box h3 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .cta-section {
      background-color: #1b75d0;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 60px 20px;
    }

    .cta-section h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .cta-section p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }

    .cta-section a {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      color: #1b75d0;
      padding: 12px 28px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .cta-section a:hover {
      background-color: #e5e5e5;
    }

    footer {
      background-color: #183153;
      color: #ccc;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .ftr {
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .ftr a {
      color: #ccc;
      margin: 0 8px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .ftr a:hover {
      color: #fff;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero-sec h2 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
      }

      .hero-sec p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      .hero-sec a {
        width: 90%;
      }

      .features {
        padding: 40px 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="navbar">
      <div class="nav-title border">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-book" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <span>LIBRARY MANAGEMENT</span>
      </div>
      <div class="nav-right">
        <form action="/login">
          <button type="submit" class="btn border">Log in</button>
        </form>
        <form action="/signup">
          <button type="submit" class="btn border">Sign up</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="hero-sec">
    <h2>Welcome to MyLibrary</h2>
    <p>Discover, manage, and borrow from a massive collection of <strong>131,860 books</strong> â€” your digital library, redefined.</p>
    <a href="/browse">Start Browsing</a>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <div class="feature-box">
      <h3>Extensive Collection</h3>
      <p>Over 131,000 books available across categories, authors, and genres.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-box">
      <h3>Instant Borrowing</h3>
      <p>Quick book issuing and seamless returns with real-time tracking.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-box">
      <h3>Personalized Dashboard</h3>
      <p>Keep track of your issued books, history, and personalized recommendations.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>Join the Digital Library Revolution</h2>
    <p>Create your account today and enjoy full access to our powerful library system.</p>
    <a href="/signup">Create an Account</a>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 MyLibrary. All rights reserved.</p>
    <div class="ftr">
      <a href="#" aria-label="WhatsApp"><i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i></a>
      <a href="#" aria-label="Instagram"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
      <a href="#" aria-label="Twitter"><i class="fab fa-x-twitter"></i></a>
      <a href="#" aria-label="LinkedIn"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
      <a href="#" aria-label="YouTube"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i></a>
      <a href="#" aria-label="Facebook"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
